    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically superlative, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory Alpine White paint remains flawless, protecting a chassis equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for precise torque vectoring. The induction note remains crisp, and the interior retains its original matte finish with no bolster wear. A definitive turn-key example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
